Lights
=======
F1 			: Enable lighting
Shift + F1 	: Disable lighting 					// DEFAULT

F2 			: Enable LIGHT0 (wall)
Shift + F2 	: Disable LIGHT0 					// DEFAULT

F3 			: Enable LIGHT1	(wall)
Shift + F3 	: Disable LIGHT1 					// DEFAULT

F4 			: Enable LIGHT2 & LIGHT3(headlights)
Shift + F4 	: Disable LIGHT2 & LIGHT3			// DEFAULT

Cameras
========
F8			: Activate camera on the wall(global view) 	// DEFAULT
F9			: Activate camera inside the vehicle(first person view)
F10			: Activate camera over the vehicle (third person view)

Movement 
=========
UP			: Move forward
DOWN		: Move backward
LEFT		: Turn left
RIGHT		: Turn right


Old key controls(asgn 2 part 1)
===============================

//Direct Transformations
C : Transform directly into car form
T : Transform directly into human form

// upper left hand
Q and Shift+Q : rotate about x axis(w.r.t torso)
W and Shift+W : rotate about y axis(w.r.t torso)
E and Shift+E : rotate about z axis(w.r.t torso)

//lower left hand
R and Shift+S : rotate about elbow

// upper right hand
1 and Shift+1 : rotate about x axis(w.r.t torso)
2 and Shift+2 : rotate about y axis(w.r.t torso)
3 and Shift+3 : rotate about z axis(w.r.t torso)

//lower right hand
4 and Shift+4 : rotate about elbow


//back wheel slab (which holds rear wheels)
F and Shift+F : rotate w.r.t torso

//Waist
M and Shift+M : rotate about y axis(w.r.t torso)

//upper left leg
P and Shift+P : rotate about x axis(w.r.t torso)
O and Shift+O : rotate about z axis(w.r.t torso)

//upper right leg
0 and Shift+0 : rotate about x axis(w.r.t torso)
9 and Shift+9 : rotate about z axis(w.r.t torso)

//lower left leg
I and Shift+I : rotate about left knee

//lower right leg
8 and Shift+8 : rotate about right knee

//front leg slabs (both rotate in sync containing front wheels)
L and Shift+L : rotate (w.r.t lower leg)

//left feet(divided into front and rear halves. rear half in attached to front half which is attached to lower leg)
K and Shift+K (front half w.r.t lower leg)
J and Shift+J (rear half w.r.t front half feet)

//right feet
H and Shift+H (front half w.r.t lower leg)
G and Shift+G (rear half w.r.t front half feet)

neck(+head)
A and Shift+A : translate neck vertical direction

//truck ceiling cover
D and Shift+D : rotate (w.r.t torso)

//front glasses(attached to both feet)
B and Shift+B : Rotate w.r.t feet

//Side gates(attached to both lower arms)
X and Shift+X : rotate about the edge of lower arm
